<div class="content" name="MInterfacePointer" uuid="21781a97-cb45-4655-82b0-02c4a1584603"><p>MInterfacePointer is an NDR-marshaled structure that MUST
contain a hand-marshaled <a href="fe6c5e46-adf8-4e34-a8de-3f756c875f31" data-linktype="relative-path">OBJREF</a>.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct tagMInterfacePointer {
   unsigned long ulCntData;
   [size_is(ulCntData)] byte abData[];
 } MInterfacePointer;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>ulCntData:</b>  This MUST specify the
size, in bytes, of the <i>abData</i> parameter.</p><p><b>abData:</b>   An array of bytes that
MUST contain an OBJREF.</p></div>